用resolve調色 首先教返好對比度光暗嗰啲 之後就調色 <br />\n<br />\n最簡單就係光位拉橙色 陰影位拉青藍色平衡 就會有電影/菲林嘅感覺 <br />\n<br />\n其次就係將成個畫面 一係拉青藍色一係拉橙色 都係一啲簡單嘅調色方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分調下調色前後:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/171211_c7dbb8c3ebf62be4e2b748ebcec1920b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F171211_c7dbb8c3ebf62be4e2b748ebcec1920b.png&h=ef0c351b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/171210_d77dfb215ab7b86715e1511185ba74df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F171210_d77dfb215ab7b86715e1511185ba74df.png&h=aa017142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/172137_445192872b5c89cbf9add222cdfdf986.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F172137_445192872b5c89cbf9add222cdfdf986.png&h=b67f5f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/172139_6f0aba04e2cc716740c95dd1ce2b57d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F172139_6f0aba04e2cc716740c95dd1ce2b57d7.png&h=fa3b2273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/172142_fbf1dfa371af7d2dd266fa93e4ea66f6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F172142_fbf1dfa371af7d2dd266fa93e4ea66f6.png&h=2c51964f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/172145_3beb42541011490922b9e16a216565b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F172145_3beb42541011490922b9e16a216565b0.png&h=44ef05ab&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"我都學緊用Resolve 謝謝分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下你點決定最光同最暗個值 我有save低你片D cap圖睇wavefrom<br />\n我見都唔會拉到0同1023!!<br />\n仲想問下點處理skintone 我見上網教有D話唔使理 有D又話跟番vectorscope條線<br />\n<br />\n好多問題 師兄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:01:53.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打鍾意我D片!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先拍片嘅時候用航拍機或者相機入邊嘅histogram功能 唔好俾畫面出現死黑或者死白 用一啲flat嘅video profile 返到去就可以調整光暗對比<br />\n<br />\n首先拉低陰影同拉高光位 望住個waveform拉 唔好拉到0同1023就得 通常光位去到896以下就得 1023附近嗰啲係屬於發光嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n拉光暗對比 最難嘅地方 就係要match每個鏡頭嘅對比同感覺 因為就算同一個地方唔同嘅shot 個曝光同對比都會差好遠!! 就要靠拉陰影 midtone 同高光嚟match<br />\n<br />\n舉個誇張啲嘅例子 第一個鏡頭係日頭仲未出晒嘅時候影 第二個鏡頭係中午烈日當空嘅時候影 可以睇到感覺完全唔同<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/164231_50a2ba8adc8b7ae33cc264853092bc60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F164231_50a2ba8adc8b7ae33cc264853092bc60.png&h=e4b1c769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/164246_5a2b3cbc01088d343a9f1d2db9909ebe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F164246_5a2b3cbc01088d343a9f1d2db9909ebe.png&h=ce6a051c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMatch完再調色 就會營造到兩個都係日落嘅感覺:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/164358_f4082c2e6f013ba03a1788189c4f853e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F164358_f4082c2e6f013ba03a1788189c4f853e.png&h=99ad3ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/164405_462951c9e8f9f988cb4d4062960565f4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F164405_462951c9e8f9f988cb4d4062960565f4.png&h=290c7e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以其實令到畫面within 0 同1023唔難 最重要嘅係統一每個鏡頭嘅 對比 光線同感覺 <br />\n<br />\nSkintone方面我唔係知好多 因為我唔會搞skintone 只要睇落正正常常就收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 通常用到vector scope處理skin tone係嗰啲有演員大頭 有對話之類嗰啲片 白平衡啊燈光等等都要控制得好 先做到咁準確嘅skin tone 相反我只係拍旅遊片 睇到個人樣正常自然就可以 同埋舉個例 日落嘅時候塊面有黃光照住 已經唔可以用vector scope整skin tone<br />\n<br />\n最後就係調色唔好用LUT住 首先會壞手勢 第二少咗好多學習同練習嘅步驟 同埋技巧唔係太純熟嘅話用LUTS 9成嘅鏡頭只會似用左ig filter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以用返人手調色會好啲 當自己調色好靚嘅時候 就可以試吓用LUTS幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分享一下我最近調色得比較重手嘅片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NkuNkdatuMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNkuNkdatuMM&d=0R7mf%2BBld8gkaJqELX1QywRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e0d564b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NkuNkdatuMM</a>"},{"pid":"428ff0b454638903732132c6bbfedd06d61685db","tid":695301,"uid":56483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b85a92596cbd2a7c9a5ec32b897ed04c7caa0acc","tid":695301,"uid":62438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80d0168c481339b4a2eb7a47c2fd6643c05db6bd","tid":695301,"uid":76627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T20:14:18.000Z","msg":"建築物果段唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意酒店穹頂接建築物穹頂個位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25626ef63ea302df22e6ace3e869929cc59fc95a","tid":695301,"uid":62438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"428ff0b454638903732132c6bbfedd06d61685db","tid":695301,"uid":56483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b85a92596cbd2a7c9a5ec32b897ed04c7caa0acc","tid":695301,"uid":6