,"msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意酒店穹頂接建築物穹頂個位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好鍾意呢幢建築物/酒店 所以整咗上面嗰段片 全段都係航拍個建築物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以都俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"我都係剪片新手，唔識俾意見，不過有少少位我覺得可以改善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 一開頭個幾個飛機shot同音樂重拍位唔係好夾，係咪特登咁樣就? 例如00:15個&quot;Dream&quot;係重拍位，我自己剪的話會係個&quot;dream&quot;字換畫面，但巴打係特登後左一秒先換? 中間動物轉場個度就冇呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n2. 媽媽行入建築物我會選擇zoom in唔係zoom out，感覺好似跟住媽媽一路行入去再接酒店lobby shot會順d，想show建築物話就咁拍wide就可以，唔需要媽媽<br />\n<br />\n3. 酒店Lobby個畫面較暗，唔係好睇到個lobby有咩吸引<br />\n<br />\n4. 建築物外面有個飛機shot應該係想影媽媽係露台遠望? 但重點去左影個鹿像，媽媽細到好似粒蟻咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1633b0029bb213ac6fe387c68b59bbd66726945","tid":695301,"uid":62438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e3c68e46f05ea948571a886a874927a9b3949ee","tid":695301,"uid":56483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25626ef63ea302df22e6ace3e869929cc59fc95a","tid":695301,"uid":62438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"428ff0b454638903732132c6bbfedd06d61685db","tid":695301,"uid":56483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意酒店穹頂接建築物穹頂個位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好鍾意呢幢建築物/酒店 所以整咗上面嗰段片 全段都係航拍個建築物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以都俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"我都係剪片新手，唔識俾意見，不過有少少位我覺得可以改善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 一開頭個幾個飛機shot同音樂重拍位唔係好夾，係咪特登咁樣就? 例如00:15個&quot;Dream&quot;係重拍位，我自己剪的話會係個&quot;dream&quot;字換畫面，但巴打係特登後左一秒先換? 中間動物轉場個度就冇呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n2. 媽媽行入建築物我會選擇zoom in唔係zoom out，感覺好似跟住媽媽一路行入去再接酒店lobby shot會順d，想show建築物話就咁拍wide就可以，唔需要媽媽<br />\n<br />\n3. 酒店Lobby個畫面較暗，唔係好睇到個lobby有咩吸引<br />\n<br />\n4. 建築物外面有個飛機shot應該係想影媽媽係露台遠望? 但重點去左影個鹿像，媽媽細到好似粒蟻咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打意見!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你提醒左我有啲剪接位做得未夠好我下次會改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過有啲位就係特登<br />\n<br />\n1. 剪接通常唔好跟住音樂拍子 因為會令觀眾留意到你嘅cut位 剪接最理想係invisible<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  動物嗰一part係特登跟着音樂剪 咁樣觀眾就會留意到一隻一隻動物咁樣換 高潮位會high啲<br />\n<br />\n2. 嗰個係establishing shot 話比觀眾聽主角嚟咗呢個新嘅地方 不過zoom out的確搞到剪接唔順暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次會諗清楚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 同意 我唔應該夾硬加落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 嗰度係影人同環境嘅互動 我好多shot都鍾意咁影 不過經過巴打提醒 我一開頭應該好近個人再慢慢zoom out會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打啲意見好中point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係你講出嚟我自己都唔知呢啲位唔係太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cba2a296de91c99c03f59cd493cd8ad30767e2d","tid":695301,"uid":62438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"350806ffd8874765cc97d6886247989c456a6635","tid":695301,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"以為係女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"點睇都係阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375bdd5462ea679acb876a272a47b51b325420cf","tid":695301,"uid":163791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:37:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> turn d 色好靚"},{"pid":"173eec30dbe7c7df2be31faa96078cd1ae6a9835","tid":695301,"uid":62438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"375bdd5462ea679acb876a272a47b51b325420cf","tid":695301,"uid":163791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:37:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> turn d 色好靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26d5492a2250427bcd7631539728a83ed4d7cc1","tid":695301,"uid":37851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"平時都留意到有d片轉場景係唔跟音樂<br />\n睇落係舒服<br />\n但其實個位係應該點拿捏？<br />\n<br />\n我都係得閒會自己拍下vlog<br />\n但剪得好慢<br />\n個故事性唔夠每次拍完都好難剪得埋<br />\n見到你由初初個段片到而家都進步唔少<br />\n可唔可以分享下你係點上網學<br />\n有無話睇開邊個網站/channel教拍/剪片"},{"pid":"201d965f26610020b0c014a2a7e68ec7de51e7c8","tid":695301,"uid":62438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e26d5492a2250427bcd7631539728a83ed4d7cc1","tid":695301,"uid":37851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"平時都留意到有d片轉場景係唔跟音樂<br />\n睇落係舒服<br />\n但其實個位係應該點拿捏？<br />\n<br />\n我都係得閒會自己拍下vlog<br />\n但剪得好慢<br />\n個故事性唔夠每次拍完都好難剪得埋<br />\n見到你由初初個段片到而家都進步唔少<br />\n可唔可以分享下你係點上網學<br />\n有無話睇開邊個網站/channel教拍/剪片"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"基本上同一個scene都要cut到冇痕跡 咁就唔使跟音樂 例如你睇戲唔會感覺到佢cut<br />\n<br />\n除非有啲位你想有特別風格 咁就可以跟着拍子彈下彈下 又或者轉場景 你都可以跟着拍子一下彈左去另一個場景 又或者高潮位 你想感覺正啲 就一個拍子轉一個shot咁樣<br />\n<br />\n個重點係 你有一啲特殊目的嘅時候 你就可以跟着拍子剪 但係正常嘅時候就唔使<br />\n<br />\n我開頭都會剪唔埋故事 返到屋企覺得素材唔夠 其實拍vlog有一樣野好重要 而且只要肯做就做到 就係要拍多啲素材 例如主角向前行嘅鏡頭 你就前中後近鏡遠鏡都拍一個 咁你返到屋企剪片 就可以喺大量素材入邊挑選啱用嘅片段 (btw每去一個新嘅地方都要影establishing shot話比觀眾聽你喺邊 轉場景好有用)<br />\n<br />\n唔使驚影得太多浪費 就係影得多先有得揀 有得試邊兩個鏡頭剪埋一齊會夾 相反影得太少返到去發現剪埋一齊原來唔夾 咁就白費心機<br />\n<br />\n拍旅遊片可以睇travel feels 另外學電影基本可以睇film riot <br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢兩個channel最有用 其餘嘅你想學咩就喺YouTube search嗰樣嘢就得 我自己就睇咗好多調色教學"},{"pid":"40f9fbd61798c56de5e1ff06414eb138f823408b","tid":695301,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T11:59:07.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"409cf1eaaf789e28e056f68239f211415968fa69","tid":695301,"uid":62438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba4247f0c712e7e110c60ed323702d5f882d1f3","tid":695301,"uid":195471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:26:26.000Z","msg":"之前冰島拍落<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dNqxzoecfzw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdNqxzoecfzw&d=0R7mf%2BBld8gkaJqELX1QywRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=85d0483e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dNqxzoecfzw</a>"},{"pid":"cd14a34d4c41051ce12e8f7dc0ada6f839821e93","tid":695301,"uid":56483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"409cf1eaaf789e28e056f68239f211415968fa69","tid":695301,"uid":62438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"最近睇左呢條土耳其片，d剪接好正<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z7yqtW4Isec&amp;t=72s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3